rows.label: qst105701_msg0001
rows.name:
This is terrible, mo!
This is terrible, mo!!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0002
rows.name:
While investigating Bahn's
letters, I discovered
something amazing, mo!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0004
rows.name:
In addition to the records in the
Avaritia Trade Guild's books...mo...

rows.label: qst105701_msg0005
rows.name:
...there are records of money
movements with unknown purposes, mo!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0006
rows.name:
Upon further investigation, I
found that after the dates of
these money transfers...

rows.label: qst105701_msg0007
rows.name:
...there were ship arrivals
and departures not listed
in the shipping logs, mo!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0008
rows.name:
Through Nilny's brilliant investigation,
I found the pilot...mo...

rows.label: qst105701_msg0009
rows.name:
...and got him to confess that he was
transporting money by ship, and that
the destination was Liberalitas, mo!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0010
rows.name:
Ahem! The name of the Special Audit
Bureau is not just for show, mo.

rows.label: qst105701_msg0011
rows.name:
I want you to help me find out
where Bahn's money went and
what it was used for, mo.

rows.label: qst105701_msg0012
rows.name: Thank you for your cooperation, mo!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0013
rows.name:
They were transporting it to
the island base Lindwurm, a
small island in Liberalitas, mo.

rows.label: qst105701_msg0101
rows.name:
To think that something like
this would be found among
my mother's letters...

rows.label: qst105701_msg0102
rows.name:
A kind Nopon would have gently
closed the treasure chest, mo.
